Our consistent iOS icon pack covers diverse theme categories and follows the guidelines from Apple. These icons are pixel-perfect at 5050 pixels and the style is outline with the base stroke being 2px. All the icons have iOS Filled version. This pack works for iOS applications with vertical lists like iOS Mail App.
This is by far our most popular icon pack. The Icons8 team created all the icons in-house, started immediately after the iOS 7 release and drawing it up to this day.
